Package: Repurp
Title: Drug Repurposing — Drug-Gene/Biomarker Interaction Network Visualisation
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Tran", "Hung", email = "tranhungydhcm@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Hung Tran [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Hung Tran <tranhungydhcm@gmail.com>
Description: Provides functions to build and visualise drug–gene/biomarker interaction
    networks for drug repurposing studies. Supports six visualisation back-ends:
    static igraph/qgraph Fruchterman-Reingold layouts (SVG + PNG export),
    interactive visNetwork HTML widgets, publication-quality ggraph tripartite networks
    (Gene × Drug × Pathway), circlize chord diagrams, ggplot2 tile heatmaps,
    ggalluvial Sankey flow diagrams, and Gene × Drug-Class dot matrix plots.
    Includes a curated reference table of 18 established atopic-dermatitis (AD) drugs
    with mechanism-of-action edges.
